# TFLite Models Directory
#
# REQUIRED: Place the following model files here before running the app:
#
# 1. mobilenet_v3_scam_detect.tflite (Visual classifier - MobileNetV3-Small)
# 2. mobilebert_scam_intent.tflite (Text classifier - MobileBERT)
#
# See README.md in this directory for detailed setup instructions.
#
# After adding models:
#   1. Run: npx expo prebuild --clean
#   2. Run: npm run android (or npm run ios)
